Retrieve the environment variables that will be provided to an app at runtime.
It will include environment variables for Environment Variable Groups and Service Bindings.

#### Definition
`GET /v3/apps/:guid/env`

#### Permitted Roles
 |
--- | ---
Space Developer |
Admin |
Admin Read-Only |
